115
00:08:46,990 --> 00:08:47,900
mengarut.

116
00:08:48,830 --> 00:08:50,310
Saya satu-satunya keluarga awak sekarang.

117
00:08:50,310 --> 00:08:51,590
Bagaimana saya boleh membuang awak ke tepi?

118
00:08:52,070 --> 00:08:54,430
Awak takutkan saya.

119
00:08:57,830 --> 00:08:59,430
Xiaoxiao,

120
00:09:00,190 --> 00:09:01,780
Saya tidak akan mengamuk lagi.

121
00:09:03,260 --> 00:09:05,430
Biarkan saya tinggal di sisi awak.

122
00:09:35,860 --> 00:09:36,740
Xiaoxiao,

123
00:09:36,740 --> 00:09:37,580
Saya...

124
00:09:40,110 --> 00:09:40,950
Hai, Chenying.

125
00:09:41,470 --> 00:09:42,310
Datang dan makan.

126
00:09:46,140 --> 00:09:46,980
Ayuh.

127
00:09:49,260 --> 00:09:50,710
Xiaoxiao telah makan banyak.

128
00:09:51,470 --> 00:09:52,310
Awak patut makan juga.

129
00:09:55,470 --> 00:09:56,590
Xiaoxiao, awak...

130
00:09:57,620 --> 00:09:59,590
Anda jarang makan banyak.

131
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:02,070
Mengapa begitu banyak hari ini?

132
00:10:03,380 --> 00:10:04,540
Biasanya,

133
00:10:05,070 --> 00:10:06,070
makanan adalah terhad,

134
00:10:06,260 --> 00:10:07,260
jadi saya tinggalkan untuk awak.

135
00:10:07,740 --> 00:10:09,110
Kali ini, Jeneral sedang merawat,

136
00:10:09,620 --> 00:10:11,140
jadi sudah tentu, saya akan makan lebih banyak.

137
00:10:18,230 --> 00:10:19,110
Adakah ia terlalu sukar?

138
00:10:20,900 --> 00:10:21,990
Umum.

139
00:10:24,020 --> 00:10:25,606
- Xiaoxiao.
- Itu bukan cara memakannya.

140
00:10:25,950 --> 00:10:26,790
Jangan gunakan tangan anda.

141
00:10:27,430 --> 00:10:28,270
Di sini.

142
00:10:34,830 --> 00:10:35,670
Buka mulut.

143
00:10:40,990 --> 00:10:41,830
Itu sahaja.

144
00:10:47,540 --> 00:10:48,380
(Bagaimana Xiaoxiao boleh)

145
00:10:48,380 --> 00:10:50,260
(makan sangat?)

146
00:10:51,350 --> 00:10:52,500
(Alangkah peliknya.)

147
00:10:58,260 --> 00:10:59,100
Simu,

148
00:11:00,020 --> 00:11:01,260
Saya sediakan hadiah untuk awak.

149
00:11:02,380 --> 00:11:03,950
Saya tidak memerlukan hadiah.

150
00:11:05,540 --> 00:11:06,590
- Saya kata…
- Ambillah

151
00:11:06,590 --> 00:11:07,863
sebagai permohonan maaf saya atas kesalahan.

152
00:11:14,900 --> 00:11:15,740
tunggu sekejap.

153
00:11:20,490 --> 00:11:24,140
♪Musim bunga datang; ais dan salji mencair♪

154
00:11:26,060 --> 00:11:31,890
♪Semua perkara terjaga, dengan angin timur♪

155
00:11:35,070 --> 00:11:39,600
♪Dalam musim sepenuhnya♪

156
00:11:42,290 --> 00:11:43,140
Saya perasan

157
00:11:43,140 --> 00:11:44,590
anda suka perkara yang lembut dan berbulu.

158
00:11:45,590 --> 00:11:46,430
Ini bulu

159
00:11:46,430 --> 00:11:47,350
daripada musang putih

160
00:11:47,350 --> 00:11:48,316
Saya memburu dua tahun lalu.

161
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:49,800
Saya tidak tahu

162
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:50,900
apa yang saya patut buat daripadanya.

163
00:11:51,710 --> 00:11:53,350
Sekarang, saya memberikannya kepada anda sebagai azimat.

164
00:11:54,260 --> 00:11:55,710
Itu sepatutnya penggunaan terbaiknya.

165
00:11:58,230 --> 00:11:59,070
Nah?

166
00:12:01,230 --> 00:12:02,070
Adakah anda suka?

167
00:12:04,030 --> 00:12:07,170
♪Izinkan saya mencintai sepenuh hati♪

168
00:12:07,310 --> 00:12:08,150
tak apa.

169
00:12:08,150 --> 00:12:10,860
♪Dalam anggun muda♪

170
00:12:11,310 --> 00:12:14,880
♪Dengan kata-kata yang ringan dan riang♪

171
00:12:14,880 --> 00:12:17,240
♪Masih bersinar terang♪

172
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:18,860
Memandangkan anda mempunyai masa untuk pernak-pernik seperti itu,

173
00:12:19,590 --> 00:12:20,590
Saya rasa Marshal Qin

174
00:12:20,590 --> 00:12:21,590
mesti bersedia

175
00:12:21,590 --> 00:12:22,470
untuk menyerang Youzhou.

176
00:12:22,900 --> 00:12:24,260
Jika rancangan anda berjaya,

177
00:12:24,620 --> 00:12:26,660
dan Chong Utara terpaksa
untuk menandatangani perdamaian,

178
00:12:27,230 --> 00:12:28,070
rancangan anda

179
00:12:28,260 --> 00:12:30,070
untuk menuntut semula

180
00:12:30,340 --> 00:12:31,190
17 Wilayah

181
00:12:31,190 --> 00:12:32,380
mungkin tidak akan menjadi kenyataan.

182
00:12:33,470 --> 00:12:34,350
Saya gembira

183
00:12:35,860 --> 00:12:36,740
awak ambil berat tentang saya.

184
00:12:50,620 --> 00:12:52,060
(Shuozhou)

185
00:12:55,740 --> 00:12:56,580
Begitu meriah.

186
00:13:18,310 --> 00:13:19,230
Xiaoxiao.

187
00:13:19,270 --> 00:13:20,140
Xiaoxiao.

188
00:13:20,430 --> 00:13:21,590
Xiaoxiao, awak hendak ke mana?

189
00:13:22,310 --> 00:13:23,393
Jeneral berkata

190
00:13:23,404 --> 00:13:24,860
orang ramai mengadakan Ritus Musim Bunga.

191
00:13:24,860 --> 00:13:25,700
Saya mahu pergi melihatnya.

192
00:13:28,310 --> 00:13:29,310
Xiaoxiao,

193
00:13:29,830 --> 00:13:30,830
bukankah anda pernah

194
00:13:31,140 --> 00:13:32,900
